  "body": "<p>Hello, I am Violeta Scrap and I want to show you a layout that I have done using the colors white, yellow and black, with some pictures of a dinner with my friends.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/72d89039a703c126.jpg?v=1782531330\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>For this Layout I have used a black and white striped paper from the collection “Hustle &amp; Heart” and I have placed a 11,5”x11,5” white cardstock basic paper, in which I have added some drops of spray paint in blue and black.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/8aceffa57c8ac7d8.jpg?v=1782531333\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I have used two photographs of 3x3,5” and another one of 3”x5”, and I have created a simple layout with different elements from the last collections of Amy Tangerine and some elements from old collections from Amy Tangerine; as I have lots of products from all Amy Tangerine’s collections.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/548b564fee2c4902.jpg?v=1782531336\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/a71e109c0a7f26d4.jpg?v=1782531339\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>For the title of the project I have used a white foam from the “Wild” Thickers pack from the collection “Oh happy life”, combined with another alphabet in black color, made from different materials.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/ad5d6d88312d7734.jpg?v=1782531341\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>As decorative elements, I have used some embellishments that I have cut from “The Little Things” paper, from the collection “Hustle &amp; Heart” and some letter that I have cut from the “All the things” paper from the collection “On a Whim”.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/7487f037d24502fc.jpg?v=1782531344\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>What’s more, I have included some transparent numbers, from an old Amy Tangerine’s collection, and as a decorative element some glossy puffy stickers in yellow and a faux suede bow, also in yellow.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/38ab24dceb160ef4.jpg?v=1782531347\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>You can create a Layout combining some elements from old Amy Tangerine’s collections with products from the new collections.</p><p>Violeta Scrap</p><p><a href=\"http://violetascrap.com/\">Blog</a> | <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/violeta_scrap/\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/violeta_scrap\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/VioletaScrap/\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/VioletaScrap\">YouTube</a></p><p>Supplies: Hustle &amp; Heart - 12x12 Double Sided Paper – In alignment (341864), Hustle &amp; Heart - 12x12 Double Sided Paper – Fit to be square (341869), On a Win – 12x12 Double Sided Paper – All the feels (378728), Oh happy life Collection - Thickers - Wild (376223), Hustle &amp; Heart – Glossy puffy stickers (341889), Hustle &amp; Heart – Faux suede bows (341893)</p><p><em>Thanks so much for sharing this adorable minibook, Violeta! Other Design Team member posts can be found </em><a href=\"http://www.amytangerine.com/blog/?category=amy+tangerine+design+team\"><em>here</em></a><em>. Check your local retailer and online at </em><em>our shop</em><em>, </em><a href=\"http://bit.ly/AThustleandheart\"><em>Simon Says Stamp</em></a><em> and </em><a href=\"http://bit.ly/2vJOlKd\"><em>Scrapbook.com</em></a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
